    "description": "Grow your career with Upstox Asia Pacific Associates! We are hiring a Investment Banker for our Varanasi team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Upstox Asia Pacific Associates:\nUpstox Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Tally\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Upstox Asia Pacific Associates!",
